OL,6,FStates of Guernsey Police Complaints
OL,7,FCommission has called for a review
OL,8,Finto how complaints are processed.
OL,10,FIn their most recent annual review,
OL,11,Fthe Commission has expressed its
OL,12,Fsupport for a comprehensive review of
OL,13,Fthe current process to inspire public
OL,14,Fconfidence.
OL,16,FHowever, the Chairman of the Police
OL,17,FComplaints Commission, Robert Jordan,
OL,18,Fclarified that the Commission has
OL,19,Ffound that "in most cases, officers
OL,20,Fhave acted with integrity and respect
OL,21,Fwhen dealing with the public."
