OL,3,CCall for review into the Guernsey
OL,4,CPolice complaints process
OL,6,FIn 2023, Guernsey Police saw 46
OL,7,Fcomplaints against lower-ranked
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,FOf those, 19 were subject to
OL,11,Fsupervised review, with 17 concluded
OL,12,Fwith 'satisfied' statements and the
OL,13,Flast two needing no further action.
OL,15,FThe other complaints were not
OL,16,Finvestigated, with seven dealt with by
OL,17,Finformal resolution, three not
OL,18,Fprogressing for various reasons, and
OL,19,Fothers being sent to the Commission
OL,20,Ffor review.
