OL,6,FThere were no complaints registered
OL,7,Fagainst senior officers last year.
OL,9,FThe President of the Committee for
OL,10,FHome Affairs, Deputy Rob Prow, said:
OL,11,F"It is reassuring that the Commission
OL,12,Fhas found most officers investigated
OL,13,Fact with integrity and respect.
OL,15,F"The Commission also rightly raise
OL,16,Fthat the law around Police Complaints
OL,17,Fdoes need review, and the Committee is
OL,18,Fcommitted to undertaking that work."
